<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Compte activé — SailingLoc</title>
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a4d8c 0%, #1a73c8 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .brand {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 48px 40px 36px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .badge {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(251,191,36,0.4);
        }
        .badge svg { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
        h1 { color: #111827; font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .subtitle { color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .info-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .info-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: #374151; font-size: 14px; padding: 6px 0; }
        .info-row span.label { color: #9ca3af; font-size: 13px; display: block; }
        .info-row strong { font-size: 14px; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0a4d8c;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #083d72; }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        .footer-dot {
            width: 8px; height: 8px;
            background: #4ade80;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="brand">⚓ SailingLoc</div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1a3a5c" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Compte confirmé !</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Votre adresse email a bien été vérifiée.<br>Vous pouvez maintenant accéder à SailingLoc.</p>
        <div class="info-card">
            <div class="info-row">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9ca3af" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <span class="label">Statut du compte</span>
                    <strong>Actif ✓</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 14px;">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#9ca3af" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
                <div>
                    <span class="label">Membre depuis</span>
                    <strong>{{ "now"|date("d/m/Y") }}</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="{{ loginUrl }}" class="btn">Se connecter</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <span class="footer-dot"></span>
        Compte activé avec succès &mdash; &copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} SailingLoc
    </div>
</body>
</html>
